description.en: Built on Komodo Chain and with a Total Supply of 210 Million Coins, Gleec Coin categorizes as an utility asset with a wide range of applications. Not only can you buy or sell Gleec Coin on several top exchanges, you can also use it to top-up your Visa Gleec Card and pay for goods and services.
